### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AUTH
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [1] Super Admin login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/super-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@corez.com", "password": "Admin@123" }

###

### [2] School user login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/school
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@dps.edu", "password": "Admin@123" }

###

### [3] Send OTP — check server logs for devCode
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{ "phone": "+916294690079" }

###

### [4] Verify OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{ "phone": "+916294690079", "otp": "683939" }

###

### [5] Registration — step 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/init
Content-Type: application/json

{ "card_number": "PASTE_CARD_NUMBER", "phone": "+919999999999" }

###

### [6] Registration — step 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nonce": "PASTE_NONCE", "otp": "PASTE_FROM_LOGS", "phone": "+919999999999" }

###

### [7] Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}" }

###

### [8] Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}" }

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### PARENT — home screen data
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [9] GET /me — full home data
GET {{baseUrl}}/parents/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### PARENT — profile update (debug version)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [10] Profile update — minimal (no doctor phone, no contacts)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/parents/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "student": {
    "first_name": "Aarav",
    "last_name": "Sharma",
    "class": "4th Year",
    "section": "CS"
  },
  "emergency": {
    "blood_group": "B_POS",
    "allergies": "None"
  }
}

###

### [11] Profile update — with doctor phone (plain Indian number)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/parents/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "emergency": {
    "doctor_name": "Dr. Suresh Kumar",
    "doctor_phone": "9876543210"
  }
}

###

### [12] Profile update — with contacts
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/parents/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "contacts": [
    {
      "name": "Ramesh Sharma",
      "phone": "9876543210",
      "relationship": "Father",
      "priority": 1
    }
  ]
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### PARENT — other endpoints
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [13] Scan history
GET {{baseUrl}}/parents/me/scans
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [14] Visibility update
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/parents/me/visibility
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "student_id": "{{studentId}}", "visibility": "PUBLIC", "hidden_fields": [] }

